descriptionHtml:
-This is my attempt at making the talented actress, Milla Jovovich. She is a Nord, and her faction is up to you to decide.-

-It\'s saved towards the beginning of the game where you have to go to Bleak Falls Barrow. 
One cheat active and that is the carryweight cheat. So if you do not like using cheats, 
download at your own risk.-

(If you want the character to look exactly like the one in the pictures, then you should download these wonderful mods.)

^_^
